│ semantics match for both GEPs. I will locate the compare-folding in InstCombineCompares.cpp, add a check that   │
│ both hasNoUnsignedWrap() and hasNoSignedWrap() are equal between the two GEPs before folding, and then submit   │
│ the patch.                                                                                                      │
